data.description: Come take a look at this affordable home in central Bakersfield. This property is located 6 minutes away from downtown Bakersfield, Mechanics Bank Arena, The Padre, the Fair Grounds,, Valley Plaza, and a variety  of restaurants. It also features quick freeway access. The spacious backyard is great for the kids, family gatherings, or for pets. The functional floor plan and garage is ideal for a first time buyer or investor looking to add to their portfolio. Come take a look before it is gone! It is priced to sell.
